name: PixelFem #2 - Patti McGee
description:
Patti McGee was the first woman to become a pro skateboarder and was immortalised on the cover of LIFE magazine in 1965, photographed doing a handstand on her skateboard.

✺This work is part of PixelFems, an evolving project on the Tezos blockchain celebrating iconic women from the past and present✺
